接口 FsBean


  • @Immutable
 @ThreadSafe
public interface FsBean
    Bean info of object, usually resolved by FsBeanResolver.
    另请参阅:
    FsBeanResolver

    • 方法详细资料

      • resolve

        static FsBean resolve(java.lang.reflect.Type type)
        Resolves given type to FsBean by FsBeanResolver.defaultResolver().
        参数:
        type - given type
        返回:
        given type to FsBean

      • wrap

        static FsBean wrap(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,?> map)
        Wraps given map as a FsBean by FsBeanResolver.defaultResolver(), of which type will be seen as Map<String, Object>. This method is equivalent to: 
             wrap(map, null);
        参数:
        map - given map
        返回:
        given map as a FsBean
        另请参阅:
        wrap(Map, Type)

      • wrap

        static FsBean wrap(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,?> map,
                   @Nullable
                   @Nullable java.lang.reflect.Type mapType)
        Wraps given map as a FsBean by FsBeanResolver.defaultResolver(), the key type of map type must be String. If the given map type is null, the map type will be seen as Map<String, Object>.

        Result of getProperties() is immutable, but content may be different for each time calling. Because of the changes in given map, contents of return property map are also changed accordingly.

        参数:
        map - given map
        mapType - given map type
        返回:
        given map as a FsBean
